<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 06:08:41 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>普京盟友承认俄罗斯对中国的依赖日益加深</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-ally-admits-russias-growing-dependency-on-china/articleshow/108031312.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108031312.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于乌克兰冲突相关制裁，俄罗斯与西方的关系逐渐疏远，俄罗斯与中国的贸易大幅增加。自2014年吞并克里米亚以来，获得人民币贷款的努力不断加强，但进展仍然有限。尽管寻求中国资本来弥补西方制裁的缺口，但财政部长安东·西卢阿诺夫承认，达成协议仍然遥不可及。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 05:17:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-ally-admits-russias-growing-dependency-on-china/articleshow/108031312.cms</guid></item><item><title>漏油事件给伊拉克农民带来压力</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/oil-spills-pile-on-pressure-for-iraqs-farmers/articleshow/108030892.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108030892.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;伊拉克拥有巨大的石油财富，但北部许多贫困的农民表示，原油泄漏污染了他们的土地，给他们已经在与干旱作斗争的压力雪上加霜。伊拉克饱受数十年冲突、腐败和基础设施破败的蹂躏，石油泄漏污染了北部省份的农田，尤其是在冬季降雨期间。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 05:00:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/oil-spills-pile-on-pressure-for-iraqs-farmers/articleshow/108030892.cms</guid></item><item><title>法国领导人表示，未来不“排除”西方军队驻扎乌克兰的可能性</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putting-western-troops-on-the-ground-in-ukraine-is-not-ruled-out-in-the-future-french-leader-says/articleshow/108029438.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108029438.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;法国总统马克龙在欧洲领导人会议后讨论了向乌克兰派遣西方军队的问题。会议未能达成共识，但马克龙强调支持防止俄罗斯侵略。人们仍然对美国的支持和特朗普重返白宫的可能性感到担忧。马克龙拒绝透露哪些国家正在考虑派遣军队的细节，称他更愿意保持一些“战略模糊性”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 04:17:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putting-western-troops-on-the-ground-in-ukraine-is-not-ruled-out-in-the-future-french-leader-says/articleshow/108029438.cms</guid></item><item><title>大多数联合国安理会成员要求塔利班废除严重压迫妇女和女童的法令</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/most-un-security-council-members-demand-taliban-rescind-decrees-seriously-oppressing-women-and-girls/articleshow/108028711.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108028711.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联合国安理会三分之二以上的成员要求塔利班废除所有压迫妇女和女童的政策。理事会谴责塔利班对妇女和女童的镇压，并坚持要求她们平等参与。特使们与塔利班讨论阿富汗路线图，强调包容性、多元化代表性和尊重人权的必要性。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 03:50:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/most-un-security-council-members-demand-taliban-rescind-decrees-seriously-oppressing-women-and-girls/articleshow/108028711.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯在莫斯科：俄罗斯作为中东调解人的角色是什么？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hamas-in-moscow-what-is-russias-role-as-mideast-mediator/articleshow/108027395.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108027395.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;哈马斯、法塔赫、巴勒斯坦解放组织等巴勒斯坦各派代表将出席莫斯科会议，就以色列与哈马斯战争、巴勒斯坦权力机构在加沙的作用以及中东问题进行会谈。此次会议旨在展示俄罗斯的影响力并支持巴勒斯坦民族团结。哈马斯自 2007 年以来一直统治加沙，被欧盟、美国和其他国家政府列为恐怖组织。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 03:20:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hamas-in-moscow-what-is-russias-role-as-mideast-mediator/articleshow/108027395.cms</guid></item><item><title>泰勒·斯威夫特的父亲被指控在澳大利亚殴打摄影师</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/taylor-swifts-dad-accused-of-punching-photographer-in-australia/articleshow/108026256.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108026256.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;当地新闻来源的报道显示，受害者是一名澳大利亚摄影师，在悉尼港夜间郊游后，她一直在中立湾码头等待泰勒·斯威夫特和她的父亲抵达。但她的父亲已经上了车。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 02:30:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/taylor-swifts-dad-accused-of-punching-photographer-in-australia/articleshow/108026256.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国总统拜登希望加沙在下周一之前实现休战</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-president-biden-holds-hope-for-gaza-truce-by-next-monday/articleshow/108025647.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108025647.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国总统乔·拜登希望下周在加沙实现停火。在巴黎会议期间达成了相互谅解。会谈正在穆斯林斋月期间进行。卡塔尔埃米尔和哈马斯领导人讨论立即停火。以色列的军事行动导致加沙地带死亡和人质。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 01:31:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-president-biden-holds-hope-for-gaza-truce-by-next-monday/articleshow/108025647.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄克拉荷马州 16 岁非二元学生死亡引发美国部分州反跨性别法的关注</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/death-of-non-binary-student-16-in-oklahoma-spotlights-anti-trans-laws-in-some-us-states/articleshow/108025482.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108025482.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄克拉荷马州一所学校卫生间发生争执，一名非二元学生向嘲笑他们的女孩泼水，导致其死亡。该事件引起了广泛关注，凸显了跨性别学生面临的危险以及解决 LGBTQ 学生权利的必要性。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 01:01:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/death-of-non-binary-student-16-in-oklahoma-spotlights-anti-trans-laws-in-some-us-states/articleshow/108025482.cms</guid></item><item><title>下议院议员指责印度跨国镇压英国锡克教徒</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/mp-in-commons-accuses-india-of-transnational-repression-of-uk-sikhs/articleshow/108021972.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108021972.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;英国议员普利特·吉尔对与印度有关的个人对英国锡克教徒进行跨国镇压表示担忧。吉尔质疑安全部长汤姆·图根哈特为解决这一问题而采取的措施的有效性。五眼国家对与印度有关的个人针对英国锡克教活动人士的攻击表示担忧。吉尔是在下议院内政部口头质询期间发表上述言论的。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 18:41:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/mp-in-commons-accuses-india-of-transnational-repression-of-uk-sikhs/articleshow/108021972.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦一名身穿阿拉伯文连衣裙的女子从暴徒手中获救</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/woman-in-arabic-script-dress-saved-from-mob-in-pakistan/articleshow/108022030.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108022030.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周日，在拉合尔繁忙的伊奇拉集市，警方迅速介入，从暴徒手中救出了一名身穿阿拉伯书法连衣裙的年轻女孩。暴民指控她亵渎神明。当300多人将这名女子强行带到附近的一家餐馆并要求她脱掉衣服时，情况变得很糟糕。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 18:50:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/woman-in-arabic-script-dress-saved-from-mob-in-pakistan/articleshow/108022030.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国反腐机构首次调查“一带一路”项目</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/chinas-anti-graft-body-to-probe-bri-projects-for-the-first-time/articleshow/108025421.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108025421.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国国家主席习近平的万亿美元贸易和基础设施一带一路倡议将因腐败指控和债务陷阱而受到中央纪律检查委员会的调查。李希领导的中纪委将把体制改革、廉政建设和司法机构建设放在首位。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 00:50:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/chinas-anti-graft-body-to-probe-bri-projects-for-the-first-time/articleshow/108025421.cms</guid></item><item><title>匈牙利批准后瑞典将成为北约成员国</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/sweden-set-to-become-nato-member-after-hungary-ratifies-bid/articleshow/108020284.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108020284.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;匈牙利议会批准了瑞典加入北约的申请，这是瑞典在俄罗斯入侵乌克兰期间加入北约的最后一步。该批准以 188 票赞成、6 票反对的结果标志着一个历史性时刻，使瑞典成为北约第 32 个成员国。北约秘书长斯托尔滕贝格对这一决定表示欢迎，强调其对加强欧洲-大西洋安全的重要性。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 16:30:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/sweden-set-to-become-nato-member-after-hungary-ratifies-bid/articleshow/108020284.cms</guid></item><item><title>为什么一名穿着“Halwa”连衣裙的女性在巴基斯坦面临暴民的愤怒</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/woman-wearing-halwa-dress-faces-mob-fury-in-pakistan/articleshow/108019811.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108019811.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在巴基斯坦，一名妇女因穿着带有阿拉伯文字的连衣裙而面临亵渎指控，被误认为是《古兰经》经文。在暴徒聚集期间，警察介入并护送她到安全地带。据澄清，剧本并不神圣。该事件反映了在严格的法律和社会压力的推动下，巴基斯坦亵渎指控的敏感性。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 16:04:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/woman-wearing-halwa-dress-faces-mob-fury-in-pakistan/articleshow/108019811.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方向战时内阁提出了拉法进攻计划</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-military-presents-a-plan-for-a-rafah-offensive-to-the-war-cabinet/articleshow/108011079.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108011079.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列总理办公室宣布，军队已提出对加沙南部城镇拉法发动地面进攻的计划。此举正值全球关注拉法局势之际，流离失所的巴勒斯坦人在那里寻求庇护。以色列的盟友强调了在打击哈马斯的战斗中保护平民的重要性。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 10:23:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-military-presents-a-plan-for-a-rafah-offensive-to-the-war-cabinet/articleshow/108011079.cms</guid></item><item><title>日本月球着陆器 SLIM 在两周的月夜后苏醒</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/japans-moon-lander-slim-revives-after-two-week-lunar-night/articleshow/108008897.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108008897.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;经过两周的月夜之后，日本宇宙航空研究开发机构 (JAXA) 成功复活了月球着陆器 SLIM。 SLIM 使用高规格相机对陨石坑进行了科学观测。尽管最初存在不确定性，但 SLIM 在度过了月夜后证实了其通信能力。 JAXA计划在仪器温度冷却后恢复运行。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 09:55:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/japans-moon-lander-slim-revives-after-two-week-lunar-night/articleshow/108008897.cms</guid></item><item><title>马克龙本周将与卡塔尔埃米尔阿勒萨尼讨论加沙问题</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/macron-to-discuss-gaza-with-qatars-emir-al-thani-this-week/articleshow/108017353.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108017353.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 13:27:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/macron-to-discuss-gaza-with-qatars-emir-al-thani-this-week/articleshow/108017353.cms</guid></item><item><title>安全消息人士称，以色列自加沙战争爆发以来首次袭击黎巴嫩巴勒贝克</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-strikes-baalbek-in-lebanon-for-first-time-since-gaza-war/articleshow/108010871.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108010871.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 10:15:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-strikes-baalbek-in-lebanon-for-first-time-since-gaza-war/articleshow/108010871.cms</guid></item><item><title>布基纳法索清真寺袭击造成数十人死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/attack-on-mosque-in-burkina-kills-dozens/articleshow/108008456.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108008456.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 09:20:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/attack-on-mosque-in-burkina-kills-dozens/articleshow/108008456.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦总理穆罕默德·什塔耶向阿巴斯总统提交辞呈</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/palestinian-pm-mohammad-shtayyeh-submits-resignation-to-president-abbas/articleshow/108008275.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108008275.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴勒斯坦总理穆罕默德·什塔耶周一宣布辞职，这是一个重大进展，为巴勒斯坦人在以色列与加沙伊斯兰组织哈马斯最近发生冲突后就政治安排达成广泛共识铺平了道路。​​此举发生之际，美国对总统马哈茂德·阿巴斯施加越来越大的压力，要求其重组巴勒斯坦权力机构。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 09:15:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/palestinian-pm-mohammad-shtayyeh-submits-resignation-to-president-abbas/articleshow/108008275.cms</guid></item><item><title>玛丽亚姆·纳瓦兹 (Maryam Nawaz) 成为巴基斯坦旁遮普省首位女总理</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/maryam-nawaz-becomes-first-woman-cm-of-pakistans-punjab-province/articleshow/108007085.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108007085.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周一，巴基斯坦穆斯林联盟（PML-N）的著名领导人、前总理纳瓦兹·谢里夫的女儿玛丽亚姆·纳瓦兹（Maryam Nawaz）成为巴基斯坦旁遮普省第一位女首席部长，实现了历史性的里程碑。 50 岁的玛丽亚姆担任巴基斯坦穆斯林联盟纳瓦兹 (PML-N) 党的高级副主席，尽管伊姆兰·汗 (Imran Khan) 的政党支持的逊尼派伊特哈德委员会 (SIC) 议员罢工，但她还是在首席部长选举中取得了胜利。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 08:41:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/maryam-nawaz-becomes-first-woman-cm-of-pakistans-punjab-province/articleshow/108007085.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>